490
00:31:13,013 --> 00:31:16,608
- 我想要下注 - 比赛已经开始了,先生
- I was trying to place a bet. - The race has started,sir.

491
00:31:19,893 --> 00:31:22,248
不能再下注,下次再试试吧
No more bets.Try the next race.

492
00:31:30,933 --> 00:31:33,925
来吧,Mostarsil!
Come on,Mostarsil!

493
00:31:36,053 --> 00:31:37,042
Christ!
Christ!

494
00:31:39,053 --> 00:31:41,567
- 1赔10,那可是50万啊! - 我没有下注
- 10-to-1,that's 500,000! - I didn't get the bet on.

495
00:31:41,653 --> 00:31:44,292
- 什么? - 我没有来得及
- What? - I didn't have time.

496
00:31:48,853 --> 00:31:50,809
那可是50万啊!
That's 500,000.

497
00:31:56,933 --> 00:31:58,048
妈的!
Shit!

498
00:32:28,373 --> 00:32:30,887
不,等等.我要看他们在做什么
No,wait.I want to see what they're doing.

499
00:32:35,413 --> 00:32:38,928
好的,他准备要上钩了 我们已经为明天准备好了
Okay,so he's gone for the bait,and we're all set for tomorrow.

500
00:32:39,013 --> 00:32:41,288
Stacie,Danny,把他卷进来吧
Stacie,Danny,go reel him in.

501
00:32:41,573 --> 00:32:43,006
有什么意见吗?
Any thoughts?

502
00:32:43,933 --> 00:32:45,764
你都已经全部掌握了
Think you've covered everything.

503
00:32:45,853 --> 00:32:47,650
那就把他卷进来
Then go bring him in.

504
00:32:52,253 --> 00:32:54,289
这次不能有错了
And no mistakes this time.

505
00:33:08,413 --> 00:33:11,291
我知道,我知道,但我在教他
I know,but I'm teaching him.

506
00:33:11,613 --> 00:33:13,444
你在窒息他
You're smothering him.

507
00:33:14,173 --> 00:33:15,891
你要给他空间
Give him his head.

508
00:33:16,773 --> 00:33:19,241
或许你会在他身上看见我所做的
Maybe you'll see in him what I did.

509
00:33:20,653 --> 00:33:22,564
而我曾经在你身上见过一次
What I saw in you once.

510
00:33:27,133 --> 00:33:29,886
我们有个问题,必须碰个面
We've got a problem,we're gonna have to meet up.

511
00:33:30,293 --> 00:33:32,761
是的,好的.6点半怎么样?
Yeah,okay.What about 6:30?

512
00:33:34,493 --> 00:33:36,688
好的,谢谢,Anthony
All right.Thanks,Anthony.

513
00:33:41,893 --> 00:33:44,361
这个国家开始围捕法律了,你知道的
This country's got stalking laws,you know.

514
00:33:44,853 --> 00:33:47,367
只是觉得我该让你知道我明天就要回去了
Just thought I'd let you know I'm heading back tomorrow.

515
00:33:47,453 --> 00:33:49,489
3点会结账离开
I check out of the hotel at 3:00.

516
00:33:49,573 --> 00:33:52,610
很好,但我还没有下决定
That's fine,but I haven't made a decision yet.

517
00:33:53,053 --> 00:33:54,771
你会来的
You'll be there.

518
00:34:00,533 --> 00:34:01,682
什么?
What?

519
00:34:01,813 --> 00:34:03,929
有的财团开始被调查了
The syndicate's being investigated.

520
00:34:04,013 --> 00:34:06,607
- 为什么? - 我不知道,好不好,但就是开始了
- Why? - I don't know,all right?It is.

521
00:34:06,693 --> 00:34:08,604
有人听到了风声,都结束了
Someone got wind of it.It's all off.

522
00:34:08,693 --> 00:34:11,332
- 不可能的 - 我告诉你了,就是
- It can't be. - I'm telling you,it is.

523
00:34:11,653 --> 00:34:14,406
他们明天会做一笔,然后就开拔走人
They're gonna do one tomorrow,then pulling the plug.

524
00:34:14,493 --> 00:34:16,324
等等,你是说他们会再做一次
Wait.You said they're doing one more.

525
00:34:16,413 --> 00:34:18,085
已经布局好了
It's already set.

526
00:34:19,853 --> 00:34:22,367
- 为什么我们不可以呢? - 你在说笑吗?
- Why can't we do it,too? - Are you having a laugh?

527
00:34:22,453 --> 00:34:25,889
权威人士会像老鹰一样盯着整场比赛的
The authorities will be watching that race like hawks.

528
00:34:26,053 --> 00:34:28,886
他们会盯着那些财团,而不是我们
They'll be watching the syndicate,not us.

529
00:34:30,213 --> 00:34:32,283
我不知道.你在想什么?
I don't know.What do you think?

530
00:34:33,293 --> 00:34:34,487
冒险
Risky.

531
00:34:38,293 --> 00:34:40,887
他不敢,就这样
He who dares and all that.

532
00:34:42,493 --> 00:34:44,563
确定这值得冒险吗?
Surely it's worth the risk?

533
00:34:48,013 --> 00:34:50,049
如果我们要做这笔...
If we're gonna do this...

534
00:34:50,733 --> 00:34:53,884
就应该是笔大的
it has got to be a big bet.

535
00:34:54,613 --> 00:34:57,081
因为我告诉你了,这是最后的机会
Because I'm telling you,this is the last chance.

536
00:34:57,173 --> 00:34:58,572
绝对
Absolutely.

537
00:34:59,613 --> 00:35:02,810
我最多只能提升到3万
The most I can raise is probably going to be about 30,000.

538
00:35:03,013 --> 00:35:07,052
开玩笑.我才不愿为这个而冒被抓住的危险呢
You've got to be joking.I'm not risking getting caught for that.

539
00:35:09,253 --> 00:35:11,323
那要多少你才肯冒险?
So how much would it take?

540
00:35:14,053 --> 00:35:15,566
50万
500,000.

541
00:35:17,853 --> 00:35:19,684
- 什么? - 50万
- What? - 500,000.

542
00:35:19,773 --> 00:35:23,402
即使只有1赔2的赔率,我们也能赚个100万
Even if we only get 2-to-1 again,we'd clear 1 million.

543
00:35:25,333 --> 00:35:28,052
我怕这超出了我的范围
It's too rich for my blood I'm afraid.

544
00:35:30,813 --> 00:35:34,852
如果有100万在银行的话,我们这个周末会非常美满的
We could have a wonderful week with 1 million in the bank.

545
00:35:35,973 --> 00:35:37,565
对不起,不
I'm sorry,no.

546
00:35:40,053 --> 00:35:42,647
好吧,如果你不能胜任...
Well,if you're not up to it...

547
00:35:43,773 --> 00:35:46,003
这不是能不能胜任的问题...
It's not a question of not being up to it...

548
00:35:46,093 --> 00:35:48,732
我只是不能一下子失去那么多钱
I just can't afford to lose that kind of money.

549
00:35:48,813 --> 00:35:50,565
你怎么会失去呢?
How could you lose?

550
00:35:50,973 --> 00:35:53,362
我是说,你都看见是如何运作的了
I mean,you've seen how it works.

551
00:35:54,773 --> 00:35:56,047
即使这样
Even so.

552
00:35:57,413 --> 00:35:58,926
50万
500,000.

553
00:36:03,333 --> 00:36:06,131
<i>这可是一生才一次的机会</i>
<i>This is a once in a lifetime opportunity.</i>

554
00:36:07,253 --> 00:36:10,563
<i>我是说,要不就是现在,要不就是永远也没有了</i>
<i>I mean,it's now or it's never.</i>

555
00:36:12,133 --> 00:36:17,082
<i>记住:"懦夫难得美人心"</i>
<i>Remember:"A faint heart never won a fair maiden."</i>

556
00:36:23,493 --> 00:36:25,848
好吧,我干了
Okay,I'm in.

557
00:36:33,933 --> 00:36:37,642
银行经理觉得我有神经病 我只能威胁要关掉我的账户
Bank manager thought I was insane.I had to threaten to close my account.

558
00:36:37,733 --> 00:36:40,645
你拿着双倍回来后他会冷静下来的
He'll calm down when you pay double back in.

559
00:36:41,733 --> 00:36:43,644
你确信他们能接受这么大的赌注吗?
You're sure they'll take a bet this size?

560
00:36:43,733 --> 00:36:45,564
你听到那个男人说的了,没有限制
You heard the man.No limit.

561
00:36:46,293 --> 00:36:48,568
先生们.觉得运气不错吧?
Gentlemen.Feeling lucky again?

562
00:36:49,653 --> 00:36:51,291
我认为没问题
I think we'll be okay.

563
00:36:51,373 --> 00:36:52,647
是吗?
Think so?

564
00:36:53,813 --> 00:36:56,088
我真是希望里面都是钱
I do hope that's full of money.

565
00:37:00,373 --> 00:37:02,568
我们很快就能把这笑容从他脸上擦掉
We'll soon wipe that smile off his face.

566
00:37:02,653 --> 00:37:04,245
不要理他
Just ignore him.

567
00:37:05,453 --> 00:37:09,526
Yvonne会通过电话告诉是哪匹马 然后和我们在这里碰面
Yvonne will phone the horse through,and then she'll meet us here.

568
00:37:10,493 --> 00:37:12,290
我去拿点喝的
I'll get us a drink.

569
00:37:24,253 --> 00:37:26,813
- 有结果了吗? - 幸运儿最后会赢
- Anything? - Favorite won the last.

570
00:37:26,893 --> 00:37:29,771
- 我们要试图取得更大的几率 - 等等
- We've gotta try and get bigger odds. - Wait.

571
00:37:29,853 --> 00:37:33,812
<i>...Kieren Fallon在Roofer和Dennis El Menace的前二,三位...</i>
<i>...Kieren Fallon has gone two or three in front of Roofer and Dennis El Menace...</i>

572
00:37:33,893 --> 00:37:35,849
<i>战争会在...</i>
<i>battling on...</i>

573
00:37:42,773 --> 00:37:44,126
明白了
Got it.

574
00:37:48,533 --> 00:37:51,411
下一场把所有的都压在Roofer上
Place it all on Roofer in the next race.

575
00:37:52,093 --> 00:37:54,084
好的,我们到时候见
Yeah,I'll see you there.

576
00:38:00,053 --> 00:38:01,042
Roofer
Roofer.

577
00:38:10,613 --> 00:38:13,286
1赔8.那可是4百万!
8-to-1.That's 4 million!

578
00:38:14,093 --> 00:38:16,812
他们都在围栏里.去押注吧!
They're in the stalls.Get the bets on!

579
00:38:19,053 --> 00:38:21,567
<i>最后一场即将开始</i>
<i>Last one to go on the inside.</i>

580
00:38:29,813 --> 00:38:31,246
你的
Here you go.

581
00:38:33,653 --> 00:38:35,644
下一场Roofer
Roofer in the next race.

582
00:38:36,693 --> 00:38:38,888
50万镑押独赢
500,000 pounds to win.

583
00:38:43,893 --> 00:38:46,487
- 有问题吗? - 稍等,先生
- Is there a problem? - One moment,sir.

584
00:38:49,013 --> 00:38:50,287
怎么了,Paul?
What's wrong,Paul?

585
00:38:50,373 --> 00:38:52,409
这位先生要下一份大注,先生
This gentleman wants to place a large bet,sir.

586
00:38:52,493 --> 00:38:53,812
多大?
How large?

587
00:39:00,213 --> 00:39:01,771
50万
500,000.

588
00:39:03,293 --> 00:39:05,409
- 赔率? - Roofer.1赔8
- Price? - Roofer.8-to-1.

589
00:39:06,093 --> 00:39:08,084
我明白这里是没有上限的
I understood there was no limit.

590
00:39:09,093 --> 00:39:11,812
- 接受这位先生的赌注 - 但我没有时间来数
- Take the gentleman's bet. - I haven't got time to count it.

591
00:39:11,893 --> 00:39:14,453
拿着箱子.如果他的马赢了,我们再来数...
Take the case.If the horse wins,we'll count it...

592
00:39:14,533 --> 00:39:16,842
然后把这里的所有都付给他
and pay out on whatever's there.

593
00:39:30,013 --> 00:39:31,571
谢谢,先生
Thank you,sir.

594
00:39:32,493 --> 00:39:34,245
非常感谢
Thank you very much.

595
00:39:41,213 --> 00:39:43,443
- 好了 - 是的
- That's it. - Yes.

596
00:39:55,733 --> 00:39:57,007
那么,你们都搞定了吗?
So,you get it on all right?

597
00:39:57,093 --> 00:39:59,368
Roofer,50万押它独赢
Roofer,500,000 to win.

598
00:40:00,293 --> 00:40:02,363
独赢?我告诉你"前两名"
To win?I told you "place."

599
00:40:04,293 --> 00:40:06,853
- 什么? - 我是说"前两名"
- What? - I said "place."

600
00:40:07,173 --> 00:40:10,131
财团主张前两名会让所有人都看不破伪装
The syndicate went for a place to throw everyone off the scent.

601
00:40:10,213 --> 00:40:13,569
那才是我告诉你的 我说了,"Roffer在前两名"
That's what I told you.I said,"Place it on Roofer."

602
00:40:13,653 --> 00:40:15,723
赛马已经结束三分之一赛程了
That horse finishes third.

603
00:40:19,853 --> 00:40:21,923
弄错了.我想要回我的钱
There's been a mistake.I want my money back.

604
00:40:22,013 --> 00:40:24,811
- 先生? - 我是想说"前两名"不是"独赢
- Sir? - I meant to say "place," not "win."

605
00:40:24,893 --> 00:40:26,121
比赛已经开始了,先生
The race has started,sir.

606
00:40:26,213 --> 00:40:27,771
我不管,我要要回我的钱!
I don't care,I want my money back!

607
00:40:27,853 --> 00:40:30,242
- 赌马规则规定... - 把我的钱给我
- House rules dictate that... - Give me my money.

608
00:40:30,333 --> 00:40:31,607
拜托,放松
Come on,take it easy.

609
00:40:31,693 --> 00:40:32,921
这里发生了什么事情?
What the hell is going on?

610
00:40:33,013 --> 00:40:35,971
你不明白.搞错了
You don't understand.There's been a mistake.

611
00:40:38,693 --> 00:40:40,809
没有弄错,先生,你的马刚输了
There was no mistake,sir.Your horse just lost.

612
00:40:40,893 --> 00:40:42,451
放开我!
Get off me!

613
00:40:42,613 --> 00:40:46,765
你不是Anthony Reeves先生吗 伙计们,来点镜头
Aren't you Sir Anthony Reeves?Boys,get some shots.

614
00:40:47,293 --> 00:40:50,012
这就是你用辉煌的握手来做的事情吗,先生?
This is what you're doing with your golden handshake,sir?

615
00:40:50,093 --> 00:40:51,606
用纳税人的钱来赌博?
Gambling with the taxpayers' money?

616
00:40:51,693 --> 00:40:53,524
我没有赌博,我不赌博的
I'm not betting,I don't gamble.

617
00:40:53,613 --> 00:40:56,446
- 这个男人在你这里下了赌注了吗,先生? - 这是机密
- Did this man place a bet with you,sir? - That's confidential.

618
00:40:56,533 --> 00:41:00,162
你能否向我们的读者解释一下 为什么你会出现在这个私人的赌博俱乐部的,先生?
Can you explain to our readers why you're in a private gambling club,sir?

619
00:41:00,253 --> 00:41:02,403
我在拜访一个朋友
I'm visiting a friend.

620
00:41:02,493 --> 00:41:06,008
你觉得纳税人应该资助你的赌博 喜好是否公平?
Do you think it's fair that the taxpayers should fund your gambling habit?

621
00:41:06,093 --> 00:41:09,051
来吧,先生,你有什么要对我们的读者说的吗?
Come on,sir,what have you got to say to our readers?

622
00:41:20,373 --> 00:41:22,807
比纳税人更重要吗,先生?
More important to the taxpayer,sir?

623
00:41:23,133 --> 00:41:26,842
这是辆好车.你也是用你的所得来供车的吗,先生?
It's a nice car.Did you fund that out of your winnings,sir?

624
00:41:42,133 --> 00:41:43,532
都在这里
There it is.

625
00:41:44,493 --> 00:41:47,644
干得好,大家辛苦了 好了,让我们离开这里
Well done,everyone.All right,let's get out of here.

626
00:41:47,733 --> 00:41:50,725
明天在Eddie的酒吧把工钱给你们.现在走吧
Wages in Eddie's Bar tomorrow night.Let's go.

627
00:41:53,493 --> 00:41:55,927
- 做得好,伙计 - 好了,伙计们
- Well done,mate. - All right,mate.

628
00:42:05,893 --> 00:42:09,203
现在一切都结束了 我有一些事情必须告诉你
Now this is all over,there's something I need to tell you.

629
00:42:09,293 --> 00:42:10,487
事情是...
The thing is...

630
00:42:19,293 --> 00:42:22,285
看看你们.就像下水道中的老鼠
Look at you.Rats in a sewer.

631
00:42:24,773 --> 00:42:28,482
视力不错吧?这是什么?激光?我听说它们很不错
Eyesight better?What was it?Laser?I hear they're very good.

632
00:42:29,453 --> 00:42:31,205
我们能为你做什么,Arthur?
What can we do for you,Arthur?

633
00:42:31,293 --> 00:42:33,204
你能为我做什么?
What can you do for me?

634
00:42:33,293 --> 00:42:35,932
你可以考虑跪下来亲我的脚...
You could try dropping to your knees,kissing my feet...

635
00:42:36,013 --> 00:42:38,243
求我不要把这墙的痛苦加诸在你身上
and begging me not to paint the walls with you.

636
00:42:38,333 --> 00:42:41,450
但我还是会满足你上次的嘴脸
But I'll settle for what you've just taken off the last mug.

637
00:42:41,533 --> 00:42:44,331
对不起,我不知道你在说什么
I'm sorry,I don't know what you're talking about.

638
00:42:48,253 --> 00:42:50,164
你们只有10秒时间
You've got 10 seconds.

639
00:43:02,853 --> 00:43:04,889
把钱给他,Danny
Give him the money,Danny.

640
00:43:15,573 --> 00:43:17,768
- 等等 - 闭嘴
- Hold on a minute. - Shut up.

641
00:43:20,133 --> 00:43:21,168
不
No.

642
00:43:25,733 --> 00:43:28,645
我恨透了他一直来告诉我 我什么时候可以说话,什么时候不可以
I'm sick of him telling me when I can speak and when I can't.

643
00:43:28,733 --> 00:43:31,611
- 我来处理这个 - 就像你处理所有的事情一样?
- I'll handle this. - Like you do with everything?

644
00:43:31,813 --> 00:43:34,964
对不起,Mickey,除非我错过了点什么...
I'm sorry,Mickey,but unless I've missed something here...

645
00:43:35,053 --> 00:43:38,966
你带我们进入了洪流中,却忘记带划水的浆
you've just led us up shit creek and forgot to pack the paddles.

646
00:43:39,053 --> 00:43:41,567
哦,所以你才会那么做,是不是,Danny?
And that's what this is all about,isn't it,Danny?

647
00:43:41,653 --> 00:43:43,564
因为你觉得你会做得更好
'Cause you think you could do better.

648
00:43:43,653 --> 00:43:47,441
你为了避免出差错而做的所有事情就是低估我
Everything you've done since you got out of nick has been down to me.

649
00:43:47,533 --> 00:43:48,522
低估你?
Down to you?

650
00:43:48,613 --> 00:43:52,128
除了那句印象深刻的鹦鹉学舌:你自己来解决它们
Except for the parrot impressions:You do them yourself.

651
00:43:52,493 --> 00:43:54,165
你是个弱智的骗子艺术家,Danny...
You were a short con artist,Danny...

652
00:43:54,253 --> 00:43:56,972
在俱乐部酒吧骗骗那些喝醉的人 直到我把你带进来
working the clubs and bars for drinks till I took you in.

653
00:43:57,053 --> 00:43:59,521
